com.raylabz.firestorm

Class Firestorm

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.raylabz.firestorm.Firestorm

  • public class Firestorm
extends java.lang.Object
    The main class of the Firestorm API, which allows basic interactions with the Firestore. Must be initialized with a FirebaseApp object using the init() method before interacting with the Firestore.
